）。","density":10457,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&ll=-2.040383%2C147.372944"},{"id":"kwz4h7qd0","geo":[0.013111,127.408825],"priority":807971,"name":"Guruapin","isFolder":false,"mid":"1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk","image":"/images/user/0/bangumi/144843/points/kwz4h7qd0-1717149599804.jpg","ep":10,"s":28,"mark":"根据地图的坐标得出正确位置应该是0°00'00.0\"N 127°18'10.0\"E附近，但由于现实中这里没有任何岛礁，故选取了距离最近的大城镇。该地位于马鲁古群岛，属于印度尼西亚。","density":1589385,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&ll=0.013111%2C127.408825"},{"id":"kwzabcff5","geo":[9.51582,138.119855],"priority":529378,"name":"Colonia","cn":"科洛尼亚(雅浦岛)","isFolder":false,"mid":"1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk","image":"/images/user/0/bangumi/144843/points/kwzabcff5-1717149927972.jpg","ep":10,"s":301,"mark":"地图中提到，是武藏号最后的被目击到地点。科洛尼亚是密克罗尼西亚联邦的雅浦州首府，位于雅浦岛。","density":193738,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&ll=9.51582%2C138.119855"},{"id":"o8at6l6f6","geo":[35.285404,139.69588],"priority":186,"name":"猿島","cn":"猿岛基地","isFolder":false,"mid":"1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk","image":"/images/user/0/bangumi/144843/points/o8at6l6f6-1726500973299.jpg","ep":1,"s":830,"mark":"虚构港口","density":3291,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&ll=35.285404%2C139.69588"}]}